#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.preprocessing.label_binarize.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.learn.preprocessing.label\\_binarize"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._label._label_binarizer.label_binarize:1 of
msgid "Binarize labels in a one-vs-all fashion."
msgstr "以一对多的方式二值化标签。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._label._label_binarizer.label_binarize:3 of
msgid ""
"Several regression and binary classification algorithms are available in "
"scikit-learn. A simple way to extend these algorithms to the multi-class "
"classification case is to use the so-called one-vs-all scheme."
msgstr ""
"scikit-learn 中提供了多种回归和二分类算法。将这些算法扩展到多类分类问题的"
"一个简单方法是使用所谓的一对多方案。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._label._label_binarizer.label_binarize:8 of
msgid ""
"This function makes it possible to compute this transformation for a "
"fixed set of class labels known ahead of time."
msgstr "该函数可以对预先已知的固定类别标签集进行此转换。"

#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.preprocessing.label_binarize.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._label._label_binarizer.label_binarize:11 of
msgid "Sequence of integer labels or multilabel data to encode."
msgstr "要编码的整数标签序列或多标签数据。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._label._label_binarizer.label_binarize:13 of
msgid "Uniquely holds the label for each class."
msgstr "为每个类别唯一保存标签。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._label._label_binarizer.label_binarize:15 of
msgid "Value with which negative labels must be encoded."
msgstr "负标签必须被编码为此值。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._label._label_binarizer.label_binarize:17 of
msgid "Value with which positive labels must be encoded."
msgstr "正标签必须被编码为此值。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._label._label_binarizer.label_binarize:19 of
msgid "Set to true if output binary array is desired in CSR sparse format."
msgstr "如果希望输出的二值数组为 CSR 稀疏格式，则设为 true。"

#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.preprocessing.label_binarize.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._label._label_binarizer.label_binarize:22 of
msgid "**Y** -- Shape will be (n_samples, 1) for binary problems."
msgstr "**Y** -- 对于二分类问题，形状为 (n_samples, 1)。"

#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.preprocessing.label_binarize.rst
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._label._label_binarizer.label_binarize:26 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._label._label_binarizer.label_binarize:32 of
msgid "The class ordering is preserved:"
msgstr "类别顺序将被保留："

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._label._label_binarizer.label_binarize:38 of
msgid "Binary targets transform to a column vector"
msgstr "二分类目标将转换为列向量"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._label._label_binarizer.label_binarize:48 of
msgid ":py:obj:`LabelBinarizer`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._label._label_binarizer.label_binarize:49 of
msgid ""
"Class used to wrap the functionality of label_binarize and allow for "
"fitting to classes independently of the transform operation."
msgstr "用于封装 label_binarize 功能的类，允许独立于转换操作来拟合类别。"

